  "text": "Starting from the trained AlexNet available for use with the Caffe library [CITATION_1] , the network was then fine-tuned. For this a new scene specific dataset of 11000 images with a variety of perturbations is created (as described in the next section). Using Caffe the network was trained with a batch size of 50 images over 50 training epochs.",
